{"tid":210934,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"粵語九粒音對RAP黎講是咪負累？","createTime":"2017-04-21T09:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T12:57:32.000Z","uid":9767,"like":20,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff9887e5a6eb6513c32f3ae45237c731df4fe1d","tid":210934,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"粵語有九粒音 對RAP填詞限制好大 因為詞靚但未必啱音 拎普通話為例 其實好容易將啲歌改歌詞 因為得四粒音 易啲MATCH 音樂天份/轉數高嘅人 例如周杰倫 唔記得歌詞都可以即時改歌詞 但粵語未必啱音 唱出黎好硬夾<br />\n<br />\n太多音俾人一種數白欖嘅感覺 未必係特色 啲人講嘅粵語RAP有陣柒味應該源自呢度<br />\n<br />\n正皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粵語真係未必適合RAP <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粵語RAP不知幾有特色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67192f85093315495535416aa2b315ef2b458a71","tid":210934,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a495830967951cdd39bf1d516f7f188d22800ad2","tid":210934,"uid":32438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:48:06.000Z","msg":"都幾事實既 <br />\n唔係話唔會有好作品 但係一定有一定程度既阻礙<br />\n但係你用普通話類比  係連登.....   rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9cd3615e9eb22f6844d80b321a410cd80a4cd0","tid":210934,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"對填詞都係"},{"pid":"aedd913605607f1beb3c079f6187cc870708df45","tid":210934,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都幾事實既 <br />\n唔係話唔會有好作品 但係一定有一定程度既阻礙<br />\n但係你用普通話類比  係連登.....   rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係諗住求其搵個少啲音嘅語言做例子 應該無事掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big